find_limbs

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
find_limbs -  This method figures out the current set of limbs on the race.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void find_limbs()
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/races/base.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method figures out the current set of limbs on the race.  A creature
is assigned one "limb" for every "hand" found in the body part array.  The
number of limbs is the number of weapons that can be held.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_limbs()

.EP

